1.11:

- Increased score size
- Added support for dynamic screen sizing
- Fixed bugs relating to score and team name sizing
- Ported to Maven dependency management
- Flashing scores on game point / match point
- Added Sky Zone Theme

1.2:
- Added support for android app controller; scores can now be changed directly from app
- Added animations and various forms of user feedback
- Increased bluetooth robustness and enforced connection protocol
- Refactored asset allocation to preserve CPU usage on reload


